mbs Commencement Schedule Fall Commencement Ceremonies Event Details Saturday  December          nCredit Union   Arena n formerly known as the UIC Pavilion  n    S Racine Ceremonies For  nApplied Health Sciences  Architecture Design and the Arts  Business Administration  Education  Engineering  Liberal Arts and Sciences  Nursing  School of Public Health  Urban Planning and Public Affairs Graduate Ceremony      AM Keynote speech by Dr  Vice Provost for Global Initiatives  the Diane v S  Levy and Robert M  Levy University Professor  and Chair of the Department of Medical Ethics and Health Policy at the University of Pennsylvania Undergraduate Ceremony      PM Keynote speech by Mr  Eric Smith  Regional President  Fifth Third Bank Chicago Student RSVP The Fall      commencement ceremonies are for graduates from the Summer      and Fall      semesters  All Summer and Fall      graduates should attend the Fall commencement ceremonies  The Spring ceremonies are for Spring      graduates only The registration deadline has passed uic edu for assistance commencement uic edu Tickets Guest tickets will only be available for graduates who have registered for the ceremonies by     pm on December   Graduates can request additional tickets as we do not foresee running out of extras Tickets are not guaranteed for graduates who miss the registration deadline       in the Montgomery Ward Gallery located on the  nd floor of Student Center East      South Halsted If you are unable to pick up your tickets in advance  it is recommended that you arrive at least one hour early Caps and Gowns The pre order deadline has passed  Students who missed the deadline can purchase regalia at the UIC Bookstore starting on Wednesday  December  th        Students will have until December   th to purchase cap   gown  The UIC Bookstore is located in Student Center East at     S  Halsted Seating Seating will be assigned by college and major  Graduates will not process in  Your seating assignment will be printed on your name card  Please bring this with you to the ceremony  You are encouraged to come early to find your assigned seat  you will be seated in the department of your first major  n Information for Faculty All faculty planning to participate in commencement must have appropriate academic attire The deadline to order regalia has passed uic edu cdavis uic edu If you are planning to attend but have your own regalia  you do not need to RSVP  Plenty of seating will be available for faculty  Faculty should be backstage at least half an hour before the ceremonies and will be processed in and seated in the first rows of seating on the floor For more information uic edu nandra  uic edu Photography gradimages com www gradimages com For additional help  call our Customer Service Department at         gradimages net giservice gradimages net Official UIC photographers will also be on hand to document the festivities  These images can be found on the UIC photo database to view order photo database Additional Information For any additional questions or assistance uic edu commencement uic edu Schedule Schedule  n nBack to main content n n n n n n Back to main content Spring Commencement Ceremonies Fall Commencement Ceremonies Forever Flames Winter      Grad Fest  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Commencement n         Contact                commencement uic edu Social Media Accounts UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 